OL,3,CEsther Ghey meets with PM about school
OL,4,Cmindfulness and online safety
OL,6,FThe mother of murdered schoolgirl has
OL,7,Fmet with the prime minister and
OL,8,Fsecretary of state about mindfulness
OL,9,Fin schools and online safety.
OL,11,FEsther Ghey sat down with and Rt Hon
OL,12,FMichelle Donelan MP to discuss her
OL,13,Fcampaigns to develop mindfulness
OL,14,Fskills in schools, and to drive better
OL,15,Fsafeguarding for children on mobile
OL,16,Fphones and social media.
OL,18,FThe meeting, held over Teams, is hoped
OL,19,Fto be the first of many to help shape
OL,20,Faction around mindfulness in schools
OL,21,Fand mobile phone use.
