OL,6,FEsther said it was "a really
OL,7,Fproductive meeting" that opened up "a
OL,8,Fpositive line of communication".
OL,10,F'How are you supposed to monitor
OL,11,Fthis?' Esther spoke to ITV News
OL,12,Fearlier this month about the pressure
OL,13,Fon parents to follow their child's
OL,14,Fmobile phone activity
OL,16,F"Approaching the meeting as both a
OL,17,Fparent and the prime minister, Rishi
OL,18,Flistened to my thoughts around both
OL,19,Fmindfulness in schools and concerns
OL,20,Fover mobile phone safety for our
OL,21,Fchildren," she said.
